      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの歌、歌わないってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re saying… you’re not going to sing my sister’s song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 6.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "…………ごめんね\nでも、それが正しい気がするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry.\nBut I get the feeling it’s the right thing to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 13.500000000000004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "………………さくらが決めることだから\n私はとやかく言わないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s your decision to make‚ Sakura‚\nso I won’t try to tell you what to do. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.866666666666674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 19.20000000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "歌いたくないって気持ちは全然ないんだよ\nむしろ、歌いたいくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that I don’t want to sing her song‚ far from it.\nIn fact‚ I really do want to sing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.566666666666677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 24.93333333333331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それじゃいつまで経っても\n私達の歌は見つからない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I do‚ then no matter how much time passes‚\nwe’ll never find our own song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.100000000000012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 30.266666666666676
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、琴乃ちゃんも自分の歌を探してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why… I want you to look for your own song‚ too‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 35.340589777628594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私の歌？\n……今まで歌ってきた歌じゃなくて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My own song?\nNot the songs I’ve been singing all this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.473923110961934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 39.87392311096193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。今までは、麻奈さんのために歌ってきた歌",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Up until now‚ you’ve always sung for Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.87392311096193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは、この前のステージできっと初めて\nお姉さん以外の人のために歌ったと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think the last performance you gave was the first time\nyou sang for anyone other than your sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.04058968226116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 50.940589682261155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "仲間のためとか、お客さんのために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sang for your teammates and for the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.94058968226116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 54.476780192057305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……そう……かもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you may be right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.47678019205731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 57.318231360117615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今度は自分の歌を探してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I want you to look for your own song now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.318231360117615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "どんなアイドルになって、どんな歌を届けたいか\n……探してほしい。私も頑張るから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ask yourself‚ what kind of idol do you want to be? What kind of songs do you want to sing?\nSeek out those answers. I’ll do my best to find my way‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.08387762705485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 69.91721096038819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.91721096038819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 71.38433113098145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんと一緒に頑張りたいの\nううん、琴乃ちゃんと一緒じゃなきゃ出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be in the struggle with you.\nNo‚ I HAVE to be in it with you; otherwise‚ I can’t do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.45099779764811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 78.61766446431477
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（再び沈黙が流れる。琴乃は迷っているのだろう）\n（今までの彼女の想いを考えれば、当然のことだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Silence falls again. Kotono is probably feeling conflicted.)\n(Considering everything she’s felt up until now‚ it’s only natural.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.58433113098144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 87.45099779764806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.45099779764811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "うん……分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7509977976481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 91.0509977976481
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 91.0509977976481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0509977976481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 93.18433113098152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "この前のステージで歌ってから、感じていたの\nこれからも、こうやって歌っていきたいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was singing on stage last time… I felt it.\nI felt that this is the way I want to keep singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.55099779764828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんのことだけじゃなく、純粋に\nアイドルという仕事を全うしたいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just for my sister’s sake but simply\nbecause I want to devote myself fully to being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.91766446431494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 107.78433113098161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "…………きっと、琴乃ちゃんなら\nそう言ってくれると思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono… I knew\nyou would say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.61766446431491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "でも……こんなこと言うのは\nワガママなのは分かってる。けど…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I know that saying this\nis a little selfish. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5713880998748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-night.webp",
